data.chText: 灵𤟥（身细长、腿长、毛滑、善跑的大赛犬）
data.enText: a large thin dog with smooth hair and long thin legs, that can run very fast and is used in the sport of greyhound racing

means: 灵𤟥(身细长、腿长、毛滑、善跑的大赛犬)

tr: a tall slender dog of an ancient breed noted for swiftness and keen sight

value.def: A greyhound is a dog with a thin body and long thin legs, which can run very fast. Greyhounds sometimes run in races and people bet on them.
value.tran: 灵犭是（身细、腿瘦长、善奔跑的狗）
